The paper proposes an architecture for a partial sum generator for constituent codes based polar code decoder, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and digital systems (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the implementation results with both ASIC and FPGA technology, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR) and embedded systems (cs.ET). Additionally, the paper deals with the design of a decoder, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
